                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000709-46-defend376 t18000709-46-punish242"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice LAWRENCE.</p>
